name: Michael Jibson
bio: Actor from Hull  - currently Victor Creel in @stonstage - Lou Coulson Associates / @thrulineentertainment / @qvoice_ltd - Founder of @hullartstrust

social_posts.post_text: Lovely Birthday weekend. Lovely friends and family. But the loveliest of them all is my @carolinesheen ❤️

I love what I do and 2022 has been a good year for it. Beards, hats, so many lines learnt and lots of lovely self tapes that didn’t go my way - but you always have put the work in! It’s the work you don’t see that makes it look easy. I look forward to sharing stuff I’ve got in the can for 2023 and jobs that are hopefully coming my way! HAPPY NEW YEAR TO ALL! 🎥 🎭

Our award winning film @thelighthouse1801 is on @bbctwo tonight at 1:15am & then on @bbciplayer for the next 28 days. Please watch/record/stream if you can. Made with not much money but a lotta love. Dir @chriscroww Producer Dave Lloyd starring me & @marklewisjones64 #TheLighthouse #film #indifilm 🎥

9 years ago this week we got to perform a one off performance of Kiss Me Kate at the Royal Albert Hall. It was a special gig. Amazing cast including @thisbendavis @alsilbs @louisedearmanofficial @tonyyazbeckofficial @jasonpennycooke and the #johnwilsonorchestra #BrushUpYourShakespeare #KissMeKate
I’m so excited about this show. #Bodies is coming very soon! Directed by @marcokreuzpaintner & @ms.haoluwang for @netflixuk & @netflix #castingby @amyhubcast

Excited to say that I’ll be playing #VictorCreel in @stonstage which begins previews 17th November at the Phoenix Theatre in Londons West End. Directed by the incredible Stephen Daldry & Justin Martin & produced by @sfpofficial & @netflixuk @netflix with a creative team of dreams. This cast is so talented & you’re in for a real treat. I love the TV show of @strangerthingstv & can’t believe I get be part of the amazing world that the Duffer Brothers & Kate Trefry have created. A year in Hawkins…and The Upside Down? #strangerthings #strangerthingsonstage

Excited to be part of this epic show! Directed by @marcokreuzpaintner @ms.haoluwang casting by @amyhubcast #Bodies  #Repost @netflixuk
・・・
Four detectives, four timelines, four crime scenes... one victim. Bodies, starring Stephen Graham, premieres 19th October only on Netflix.

Here’s the full length trailer for #Bodies. It drops on @netflixuk next week - the 19th October and I hope you watch it! Filmed in and around #Leeds #York & my home town #Hull @visithulluk  @princesquayhull Directed by @marcokreuzpaintner & @ms.haoluwang. Produced by @sliggat. DOPs @joeldevlindp & @paul_morrisdp. Cast by @amyhubcast starring @sallyamaka @stephengraham1973 @4tunelloyd @shirahaas @kyle_soller @georgemparker @gabehowell @tom_mothersdale @nitin.ganatra @msemilybarber @alexandraroach1 @marklewisjones64 plus many more! Can’t wait for you to see this!!!!! #netflix #dccomics

It’s the weekend and #Bodies on @netflixuk & @netflix is out there and smashing it. Thanks for all the lovely comments & messages. Such a lovely time making this with the huge team. @marcokreuzpaintner & @ms.haoluwang  have nailed it and everyone else was a dream! #bodiesnetflix #netflix #limitedseries 🎥

Three Mills Studios is a place where TV and Film is created, it’s also where we had enough space to rehearse this massive play. This was the final few days of our rehearsals and final run through. All the team came along to watch - including the Duffer Brothers!! Slowly we piece together this new story and watch the mammoth creative team shape the show and work their magic. Now we’re in the theatre and day by day we tech the show with lights, scenery, costumes and perseverance, so that it’s ready for an audience in November. That’s when we find out what we’re in, what this play is to the people who come to see it. Stephen Daldry, @sfpofficial and team are cooking up a very special experience. Get ready for Hawkins to explode onto the West End. Stranger Things - The First Shadow @stonstage is nearly there! #strangerthings #strangerthingsonstage
We opened @stonstage tonight and this is just one of the ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ reviews. Proud of all the hard work everyone has put in. Now for a year of theatre. #strangerthingsthefirstshadow
Theatre posters just got really cool! 😎 @stonstage is OPEN! #strangerthingsthefirstshadow #theatre #Theater #theatregeek #theatreposter #theatergeek

Opening night for @stonstage was a great success. Lots of excellent reviews and it seems our “little” show is now the talk of the town. We’re now officially open so book your tickets to see #strangerthingsthefirstshadow. I was very lucky be dressed by @ozwald_boateng. Thanks to @pippygill and @pipgillentertainment for always looking after me. 🕷️💥🤩🎉⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️
